OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FTributes have been paid to Moya
OL,7,FBrennan, the iconic singer in the
OL,8,FIrish folk band Clannad, after her
OL,9,Fdeath at 73.
OL,11,FThe iconic musician and songwriter
OL,12,Fplayed the harp with the Grammy award-
OL,13,Fwinning Celtic fusion pioneers.
OL,15,FA family statement said she died
OL,16,Fpeacefully "surrounded by loved ones".
OL,26,@xD@LOUxD@eO]
