OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FThe band ` siblings Ciaran, Pol and
OL,7,FMoya Brennan and their twin uncles
OL,8,FNoel and Padraig Duggan ` achieved
OL,9,Fhuge international success over their
OL,10,F40-year career.
OL,12,FTheir distinctive and haunting sound
OL,13,Fhas sold more than 10 million albums
OL,14,Fworldwide and Moya Brennan later had a
OL,15,Fsolo career.
OL,17,FClannad formed in the early 1970s with
OL,18,Fregular performances at the family's
OL,19,Fmusic pub, Leo's Tavern, in Gweedore,
OL,20,FCounty Donegal.
OL,26,@nD@YrpnD@^rwpD@Krp
