PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776258665
OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FAnother of the Brennan siblings, Enya,
OL,7,Fleft the group in 1981 to embark on a
OL,8,Fhugely successful solo career.
OL,10,FTheir unique take on traditional Irish
OL,11,Fsongs, coupled with influences from
OL,12,FThe Beatles to the Beach Boys, won
OL,13,Fthem a folk festival competition and a
OL,14,Frecord deal.
OL,16,FTheir breakthrough hit Harry's Game,
OL,17,Ftheme track to the TV series of the
OL,18,Fsame name, came in 1982.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
