PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776258665
OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FWorldwide acclaim and a global touring
OL,7,Fschedule followed, with a string of
OL,8,Falbums and well-known hits including
OL,9,FIn A Lifetime, with Bono.
OL,11,FClannad reformed in 2011, with three
OL,12,Fcomeback performances at Dublin's
OL,13,FChrist Church Cathedral, before
OL,14,Frecording a new album and touring
OL,15,FEurope.
OL,17,FThey picked up a lifetime achievement
OL,18,Faward at BBC Radio 2's Folk Awards in
OL,19,F2014.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
