PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776258665
OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FHer musical night, Clubeo -an open
OL,7,Fstage for local musicians in her
OL,8,Ffamily pub Leo's Tavern ` was
OL,9,Fdescribed as her proudest endeavour.
OL,11,FThe Taoiseach Micheal Martin said:
OL,12,F"Deeply saddened at the passing of
OL,13,FMoya Brennan ` an iconic Irish voice.
OL,15,F"Along with her Clannad bandmates,
OL,16,FMoya brought Irish folk music to the
OL,17,Finternational stage.
OL,19,F"Deepest sympathies to Moya's family
OL,20,Fand friends at this difficult time."
OL,26,@sD@TrptD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU|D@dO]
