PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1776258665
OL,3,CClannad singer and music icon Moya
OL,4,CBrennan dies aged 73
OL,6,FThe Tanaiste Simon Harris paid tribute
OL,7,Fto Brennan, saying: "Deeply saddened
OL,8,Fto hear of the passing of Moya
OL,9,FBrennan. She was a musical icon with a
OL,10,Funique voice of extraordinary beauty.
OL,12,F"She went from Gweedore to global
OL,13,Frenown with Clannad, bringing Irish
OL,14,Fmusic to the international audience."
OL,26,@nD@FrpoD@UOUtD@AOUvD@eO]
